jo mnu`K (pRBU nwlon peI) iv`Q nUM mukw ky (Awpxy mn nUM pRBU dI Xwd ivc) joVdw hY,
aus Xwd dI brkiq nwl (sMswrk) fr dUr kIiqAW aus nUM pRBU qy SrDw bx jwNdI hY[
jo prmwqmw swry jgq ivc ivAwpk hY, aus nUM auh Awpxy AMdr v`sdw jwx lYNdw hY,
(qy ijaun ijaun) ieh rwz aus nUM KulHdw hY (ik AMdr bwhr hr Qwn pRBU v`s irhw hY) auh isRStI dy mwlk-pRBU nwl (Xwd dI) swnJ pw lYNdw hY ]30]
jy jgq dy mUl-pRBU nUM Awpxy mn ivc vsw leIey, qW mn Btkxon ht jwndw hY[
jo jIv ieh Byq pw lYNdw hY (ik pRBU-crnwn ivc juiVAW mn itk jwndw hY) auh jIv mn (dI dOV-B`j) nUM smJ lYNdw hY[
(so,) jy mn (pRBU-crnwn ivc) juVn l`gy qW mqW koeI (ies kMm ivc) iF`l kry;
(ikaunik pRBU-crnwn ivc juVn dI brkq nwl) mn (pRBU ivc) lIn ho jwndw hY, Aqy aus sdw-iQr rihx vwly pRBU nUM pRwpq kr lYNdw hY ]31]
(hryk jIv dw jgq ivc Awaux dw Asl) kMm mn nwl hY (auh kMm ieh hY ik jIv Awpxy mn nUM kwbU ivc r`Ky)[ mn nUM v`s ivc kIiqAW hI (jIv nUM Asl mnorQ dI) kwmXwbI huMdI hY[
kbIr AwKdw hY (ik jIv dw Asl kMm) inrol mn nwl hI hY, mn vrgw (jIv nUM) hor koeI nhIN imilAw (ijs nwl ies dw Asl vwh pYndw hovy) ]32]
(mwieAw nwl iml ky) ieh mn mwieAw (dw rUp) ho jwndw hY[ (AnMd-srUp hrI nwl iml ky) ieh mn AnMd-srUp hrI bx jwndw hY[
(srIr nwl juV ky) ieh mn srIr-rUp hI ho jwndw hY (Bwv, Awpxy Awp nUM srIr nwlon v`Krw nhIN smJdw, Awpxy krq`b Kwxw-pIxw hI smJdw hY)[
pr jdon mnu`K ies mn nUM v`s ivc kr ky pUrn iKVwau ivc itkdw hY,
qdon auh swry jgq ivc ivAwpk pRBU dIAW hI g`lwn krdw hY ]33]
(hy BweI!) jy qUM (jIvn dw shI rsqw) jwnxw cwhuMdw hYn, qW (AwpxI) BYVI m`q nUM mukw dyh, ies srIr (-rUp) ipMf nUM (Awpxy) v`s ivc ilAw (Bwv, A~K kMn Awidk igAW-ieMdirAW nUM ivkwrwn vl nwh jwx dy)[
(ies srIr nUM v`s ivc ilAwauxw, mwno, iek ju`D hY) jy qUM ies ju`D ivc ru`J ky Bwnj nwh Kw jweyn qW hI qyrw nwm sUrmw (ho skdw) hY ]34]
ijs mnu`K ny mwieAw dy suAwd nUM iP`kw ijhw smJ ilAw hY,
aus ny mwiek csikAW qoN bcy rih ky auh Awqmk AWMd mwx ilAw hY[
ijs ny ieh (dunIAw vwly) csky C`f id`qy hn, aus nUM auh (pRBU dy nwm dw) AnMd pRwpq ho igAw hY;
(ikaunik) ijs ny auh (nwm-) rs pIqw hY aus nUM ieh (mwieAw vwlw) suAwd cMgw nhIN l`gdw ]35]
jy (iksy mnu`K dw) mn AijhI iekwgRqw nwl (pRBU dI Xwd ivc) ibrqI joV ley,
ik iksy hor pwsy vl nwh Btky qW aus nUM sB qoN au~cw qy sdw-iQr rihx vwlw pRBU iml pYndw hY;
Aqy jy aus ilv dI hwlq ivc pRym dI qwr lw dyvy (Bwv, iek-qwr mgn rhy)
qW aus Al`g pRBU nUM auh l`B lYNdw hY qy l`B ky sdw leI aus dy crnwn ivc itikAw rihMdw hY ]36]
(hy BweI!) sdw pRBU nUM (Awpxy ihrdy ivc) Xwd r`K ky-
(jIv mnu`Kw jnm dI bwzI) hwr ky nhIN Awaundw[
mYn aus Bgq jn qoN sdky hwn jo pRBU dy gux gwNdw hY[
pRBU nUM iml ky auh hr Qwn sdw-iQr rihx vwly pRBU nUM hI vyKdw hY ]37]
(hy BweI!) aus pRBU nwl hI jwx-pCwx krnI cwhIdI hY[ aus pRBU nwl swnJ pwieAW ieh jIv (aus pRBU dw rUp hI) ho jwndw hY[
jdon ieh jIv qy auh pRBU iek-rUp ho jwndy hn, qW iehnwN imilAW nUM koeI hor nhIN smJ skdw (Bwv, iPr koeI hor iehnwN imilAW ivc iv`Q nhIN l`B skdw) ]38]
cMgI qrHW aus prmwqmw dI sMBwl kro[
Awpxy mn nUM auhnwn bcnwn ivc ilAw ky joVo, ijn@W krky ieh mn prmwqmw ivc prc jwey[
pRBU ivc mn pricAW jdon (AMdr) pRym pYdw huMdw hY,
qW aus AvsQw ivc iqMnwn Bvnwn dw mwlk-prmwqmw hI (hr Qwn) ivAwpk id`sdw hY ]39]
jy koeI mnu`K prmwqmw dI Bwl ivc ru`J jwey,
(ies qrHW) jo BI mnu`K pRBU nUM l`B lYNdw hY auh muV jMmdw mrdw nhIN[
jo koeI jIv pRBU dy guxwn nUM smJ ky auhnwn nUM muV muV cyqy krdw hY,
auh sMswr-smuMdr qoN pwr lMGidAW icr nhIN lwndw ]40]
auh (jIv-iesqRI AwpxI ihrdw-rUp) Ksm-pRBU dI syj svwrdI hY,
auhI (jIv-) sKI (Awpxy mn dy) sMsy dUr krdI hY,
ijhVI (jIv-iesqRI dunIAw vwly) hoCy suK C`f ky (pRBU dy ipAwr dw) sB qoN au~cw suK hwsl krdI hY[
(ies AvsQw dy bixAW hI AslI Bwv ivc) qdon ieh (jIv pRBU dI) iesqRI, qy auh (pRBU jIv-iesqRI dw) Ksm AKvwaundw hY ]41]
jIv ny mnu`Kw-jnm hwsl kr ky aus pRBU nUM nhIN pCwqw, jo s`c-mu`c hsqI vwlw hY[
jdon jIv nUM pRBU dI hsqI dw inScw ho jwndw hY, qdon hI ies dw mn (pRBU ivc) pqIj jwndw hY[
(prmwqmw) hY qW zrUr (pr ies ivSvws dw lwB qdon hI huMdw hY) jdon koeI jIv (ies g`l nUM) smJ ley[
qdon ieh jIv aus pRBU dw rUp hI ho jwndw hY, ieh (v`KrI hsqI vwlw) nhIN rih jwndw ]42]
swrw jgq iehI AwKdw iPrdw hY (Bwv, iesy lwlsw ivc Btkdw iPrdw hY) ik mYn (mwieAw) swnB lvwn, mYn (mwieAw) iek`TI kr lvwn[
ies mwieAw dI ^wqr hI (iPr jIv nUM) bVw &ikr Aw vwprdw hY[
pr jdon jIv mwieAw dy pqI prmwqmw nwl pRIq joVdw hY,
qdon (ies dw) &ikr mu`k jwndw hY, qy ieh swry suK hwsl kr lYNdw hY ]43]
mridAW KpidAW jIv dy keI jnm lMG gey hn;
pr, gyV ivc ipAw Ajy qk ieh (pRBU nUM) Xwd nhIN krdw[
hux (AYs jnm ivc hI) jy jgq dI AslIAq nUM smJ ky (ies dw) mn (pRBU ivc) itk jwey,
qW ijs pRBU qoN ieh ivCiVAw hoieAw hY, aus ivc ies nUM itkwxw iml skdw hY ]44]
(jgq ny) bvMjw A~Kr vrq ky pusqkwn qW ilK id`qIAW hn,
